        <Parent_String>bellows (fire controlling equipment) [300024643], fire-making and controlling equipment [300024642], temperature control equipment [300434522], cooling, heating and humidifying equipment [300163291], equipment by process [300024659], equipment [300122241], Tools and Equipment (hierarchy name) [300022238], Furnishings and Equipment (hierarchy name) [300264551], Objects Facet [300264092]</Parent_String>
